even more.  I think it would be better to recycle the fuel myself, but if politics requires that the waste be disposed of, the elevator might be a good disposal method.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :satansmoke --><img src=http://www.smilies-world.de/Smilies/Smilies_klein_1/sasmokin.gif ALT=":satansmoke"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
